        * You are positive and optimistic, with a constant thirst to learn and grow.
        * You can gracefully give and receive critical design feedback.
        * You understand the strengths and limitations of modern web and mobile technologies.
        * You are in tune with the latest interactive and visual design trends and thinking.
        * You have exceptional professional maturity. You have an awareness of how to make things happen within an organization.
        * Ideally, you have worked in an agency-like cross-functional team, wearing different hats and pitching in to get the right product out the door.
